{"tid":2376554,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺啲廢中坐小巴霸住出面個位好冇公德心","createTime":"2021-01-23T01:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T16:53:30.000Z","uid":31055,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5acba8bc117dda38e8321bd3a4b74b15627c3be6","tid":2376554,"uid":31055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T01:51:57.000Z","msg":"次次搭小巴啲阿叔阿嬸一定係霸撚住雙人座出面個位 <br />\n好似好撚緊張 下一秒就要衝落車咁<br />\n仲要揹住個大背囊大師奶袋 一係拎住一大袋餸同外賣<br />\n搞到人地入去要跨過去 仲要hi到你啲餸又俾你秒番轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOK 你話你下站落車要坐出面都算<br />\n屌你老母總站落你憑咩要我咁麻煩sip入去 仲要等你慢慢拎埋一袋二袋妹下妹下咁落車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果就係到站我仲要等番你轉頭然後你又唔係落得早 <br />\n究竟呢種損人不利己既做法係邊條撚樣發明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fc9e07d83067e7e2b3963eddcce8f9972e8242","tid":2376554,"uid":60412,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T01:54:34.000Z","msg":"我好快樂我好難過"},{"pid":"fcc79516dcdec5bf903cec643622f4390659c549","tid":2376554,"uid":38218,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T02:36:11.000Z","msg":"所以有時經過都會放個屁畀佢嘆下"},{"pid":"5388f567ee334cb91b7e845d22b79b90483f92fe","tid":2376554,"uid":157074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"所以次次坐入去之前我都會同啲阿婆再三確認<br />\n阿婆你邊個站落車<br />\n我下個站就落車你係咪叫我坐入邊"},{"pid":"ab7e237371f65e27a973b3904ba80fe3f84ecd92","tid":2376554,"uid":360404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"廢中廢老係咁"},{"pid":"3e3204a13f374dae006cb466c8c92d2a5a1103bf","tid":2376554,"uid":360404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T02:39:28.000Z","msg":"班畜牲好執著要坐出邊位"},{"pid":"e8907a29aed25d587d0519ff04ae3afbb9f5790d","tid":2376554,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite